'''Siren''' was a term used to describe dangerous, predatory "sex goddesses." These [[Gender/Legends|females]] often wore low- and/or high-cut clothing. According to [[Lando Calrissian/Legends|Lando Calrissian]], sirens had provocative eyes and many secrets.

